    <string name="desc1">BillsTracker is an app monitoring your payments making you well informed about your expenses in the way of global point of view. Collected data are being classified and shown sorted in the first part of this app. In the second one stored payment records are being summarized and represented with charts inspecting them with their dependencies.</string>
    <string name="desc2">This app was designed with emphasis on simple user-interface providing as easy usage as possible. Keeping records means a duty coming with laziness of observing this principle. This app should lend you a helping hand with it through a simple UI and easy usage that are its main priorities, besides clean design.</string>
